PREDICT

  The `clutils predict` command is used to call the prediction API
  for Custom Text or Text Analytics on documents
  in source storage and stores the prediction result in destination storage.

USAGE: clutils predict [...]

  STORAGE
    --source <local/blob>                                   (Required: storage to read documents from)
    --destination <local/blob>                              (Required: storage to write prediction result to)

  PREDICTION SERVICE
    --cognitive-service <customtext/textanalytics/both>     (Required: cognitive service used for prediction)
  CHUNKING
    --chunk-type <char/page/section>                        (Optional: select document chunking method)


SEE ALSO

  clutils help predict examples
  clutils help predict documentation